CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, August 22, 1964, pg. 6 reads: Mr. and Mrs. Clifton Victor Simmons - Harris Photo...Miss Barbara Jean Smith and Clifton Victor Simmons were married in a fashionable double ring rites at Ebenezer Baptist Church."
TitMainTitle: Wedding party of six bridesmaids, including Yvonne Turrentine, Barbara Dunn, Patricia Chavis, Marian Coon, Janet Munday, and Lois Jones, bride Barbara Jean Smith Simmons, groom Clifton Victor Simmons, man and three other women, posed underneath crepe paper streamers in basement of Ebenezer Baptist church
